defaultDame Patricia Hodgson:default There are many unknown developments in relation to Scottish independence.  If that does not happen, there is devolution, European changes in regulation—it is very difficult to predict what the balance of requirements will be.  
defaultOfcom
default is such a fast-moving political and 
defaultsectoral
default situation.  
default&#xa0;
defaultQ18 default&#xa0; 
defaultMr Leech:default This job is a three-day-a-week job.  Why is it a three-day-a-week job and not a five-day-a-week job?
defaultDame Patricia Hodgson:default It varies of course.  It can, as it was at times last year for Colette Bowe, be more than three days a week.  It is the distinction between the role of the non-executives, who really must make sure they are in a position to take an overview and to see the wood for the trees, and the position of the executives, who are working certainly more than five days a week, in my observation, but are engaged in the day-to-day managerial and operational role.  There is a danger in non-executives being drawn too close to the detail, 
defaultbecause they do then tend not to see the bigger picture, which is what this Committee and the public expect them to focus on and take action if something is astray.
default&#xa0;
defaultQ19 default&#xa0; 
defaultMr Leech:default 
defaultOfcom
