defaultQ27 default&#xa0; 
defaultAngie Bray:default You touched on switching, and also touched on the fact that you think that competition is the biggest issue.
defaultDame Patricia Hodgson:default Pressure.
defaultAngie Bray:default Pressure, exactly.  Of course, switching is all about that.  I know 
defaultOfcom
